## Proposed Changes

### 1. Smart Question Importer (`FIA Smart Question Importer Ai.md`)

We will add a new backend route `POST /api/questions/import-ai` that reads `.docx` files (using `mammoth`) or `.txt` files, extracts raw text, sends it to the Google Gemini API with a strict structured JSON schema, and returns parsed questions.
On the frontend (`client/src/pages/admin-questions.tsx`), we will add a premium "AI Smart Importer" modal where teachers select global metadata (Class, Term, Exam Type, Subject, Department), upload a file, preview a gorgeous review grid with highlighted validation states, edit questions inline, and finalize import to the database.

