### 2. High-Aesthetic Analytics Dashboard (`Cbt Anaylsis Intelligent.md`)

We will create a new, state-of-the-art super admin and teacher Analytics panel at `/admin/analytics` and student diagnostics layout on their result dashboard.

#### [NEW] [admin-analytics.tsx](file:///c:/Users/PC/Fia-Cbt-main/fgsigbohocbtv1/client/src/pages/admin-analytics.tsx)
A masterfully designed dashboard loaded with interactive charts (using `recharts`) showing deep insights:
- **Item Analysis (Psychometrics)**:
  - *Difficulty Index ($p$-value)*: Formula $p = \frac{\text{Correct}}{\text{Total}}$ flagged: Easy ($p > 0.85$), Sweet Spot ($0.30 - 0.70$), Hard ($p < 0.20$).
  - *Discrimination Index ($d$)*: Categorized: Excellent ($d > 0.30$), Useless ($d \approx 0$), Negative/Flawed ($d < 0$). Shows teachers which questions are trick questions.
- **Time Tracking & Pacing**:
  - Visual pacing distributions, flagging speed guessing anomalies.
  - Cognitive fatigue line chart comparing response time changes over active session progression.
- **Cohort Analysis**:
  - Grade distribution curve (Bell Curve).
  - Subject and topic-level mastery heatmaps.
- **System Health & Server Telemetry**:
  - Live active session count, database endpoint roundtrip latency, client-side error drop-offs, and simple load capacity gauges.

#### [MODIFY] [exam-result.tsx](file:///c:/Users/PC/Fia-Cbt-main/fgsigbohocbtv1/client/src/pages/exam-result.tsx)
- Add a new "Personal Diagnostic Insights" tab/accordion at the top of the student's result:
